subject: Move libavsysaudio to a subpackage
commitMessage:
Move libavsysaudio to a subpackage

avsystem is not functional on all profiles. Therefore, it makes no sense
to install avsystem binaries and (systemd) init scripts always.

Move libavsysaudio to a subpackage to accommodate dependencies from
other libraries. If full avsystem functionality is desired, avsystem
package must explicitly be installed.

Change-Id: Iccffd822e6bbf34f25ec1e7cda0672978da73f40
Signed-off-by: Mikko Ylinen <mikko.ylinen@intel.com>
